6
00:00:35,220 --> 00:00:41,876
♪Perhaps love
will blossom with the next spring♪

7
00:00:42,385 --> 00:00:45,520
♪Yet I can't help but feel the ache♪

8
00:00:45,636 --> 00:00:51,730
♪For you're no longer mine♪

9
00:00:52,741 --> 00:00:54,220
=Misaligned Lover=

10
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:55,300
=Episode 18=

11
00:00:55,300 --> 00:00:56,872
(Adapted from
a Himalaya Qiji Literature novel)

12
00:00:56,872 --> 00:00:58,280
(Written by Xiang Bei, author
of Heard You Got a Dog Outside? Divorce!)

13
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,490
Chenxi.

14
00:01:00,680 --> 00:01:01,730
It's me.

15
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,810
It's you.

16
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,050
You scared me.

17
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,599
I was calling over to you over there.

18
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,170
You didn't hear me, that's why I came.

19
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:10,050
It's alright.

20
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,399
They said

21
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,759
You declined the movie

22
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,850
for me.

23
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:19,930
Yes.

24
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:21,050
Did you really?

25
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:24,210
Actually, you didn't have to
do this for me. You know me.

26
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,370
I'm just kidding.

27
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:29,130
Don't believe those rumors.

28
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,799
Don't forget.

29
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,159
I abandoned you

30
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,610
for my debut.

31
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,719
How could I give up a movie project

32
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,610
for you?

33
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,130
That's good.

34
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,290
Let's go.

35
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,390
(Hope for a great start)

36
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:50,030
(Misaligned Lovers)

37
