What's wrong?

137
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,330
I'm going to kill her.

138
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,090
I can't let him hurt Mr. Lidong.

139
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,170
Aunty Zhang.

140
