I'm worried that Yu Ling
will be in danger out there at night.

141
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,679
I'll check on her.

142
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,039
Miss.

143
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,770
You can't go, Miss.

144
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,690
